{
  "id": "5a715166d56e720014822a99",
  "title": "次元の呪い",
  "created": 1517375851,
  "updated": 1588912592,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5a715166d56e720014822a99",
      "text": "次元の呪い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517375851,
      "updated": 1517375851
    },
    {
      "id": "5a715190aff09e0000a155a5",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a584556b87390d4fbad2747e235a0017]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517375888,
      "updated": 1517375888
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719d70aff09e0000a1560e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395312,
      "updated": 1517395312
    },
    {
      "id": "5a71516aaff09e0000a155a3",
      "text": " 人間は2～4次元を超えるとイメージすることが困難になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517375851,
      "updated": 1517375953
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7151aeaff09e0000a155a7",
      "text": " 次元が高くなった時に色々と意外な現象が起こる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517375919,
      "updated": 1517375970
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c89aff09e0000a15604",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395082,
      "updated": 1517395082
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c89aff09e0000a15603",
      "text": "\t高次元空間において、ほとんどすべての点は中心から遠い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395082,
      "updated": 1517395094
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c96aff09e0000a15605",
      "text": "  1次元で原点から距離1以内にある点は、距離2以内にある点の半分",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395094,
      "updated": 1517395133
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719cbeaff09e0000a15606",
      "text": "  2次元では1/4",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395134,
      "updated": 1517395138
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719cc6aff09e0000a15607",
      "text": "  3次元では1/8",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395143,
      "updated": 1517395146
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719cdcaff09e0000a15609",
      "text": "  …と次元が上がるにつれて指数的に「近い点の割合」が小さくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395164,
      "updated": 1517395181
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719d0aaff09e0000a1560a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395211,
      "updated": 1517395211
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719d0aaff09e0000a1560b",
      "text": "\tサンプリングに必要なサンプル数が指数的に増える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395211,
      "updated": 1517395220
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719d1eaff09e0000a1560c",
      "text": "  機械学習の場合に、次元を増やすことによってかえって精度が悪化する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395230,
      "updated": 1517395270
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719d4baff09e0000a1560d",
      "text": "  次元追加による精度向上よりもサンプル数不足の効果の方が圧倒的になるから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395276,
      "updated": 1517395290
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c0baff09e0000a155fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517394955,
      "updated": 1517394955
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c0daff09e0000a155fd",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/934a40866acc18c6b266fdbb0c8b1ac2]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517394957,
      "updated": 1517394957
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c44aff09e0000a155fe",
      "text": "[カイ二乗分布 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%AB%E3%82%A4%E4%BA%8C%E4%B9%97%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395012,
      "updated": 1517395013
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c0baff09e0000a155fb",
      "text": " 3次元以上の場合はベクトルの長さの最頻値が0ではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517394955,
      "updated": 1549959937
    },
    {
      "id": "5c628302aff09e000049a159",
      "text": " \t各軸が0が最頻値の標準正規分布に従うという条件",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549959938,
      "updated": 1549959957
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6282e2aff09e000049a158",
      "text": "\t [カイ二乗分布]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1549959906,
      "updated": 1549959953
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4df45aff09e00000c8d19",
      "text": "\t これは「ほとんどの点は中心から遠い」と関連している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588911941,
      "updated": 1588911967
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c5faff09e0000a15602",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395039,
      "updated": 1517395039
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719c5faff09e0000a15601",
      "text": "\tほとんどすべてのベクトルは直交する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395039,
      "updated": 1517395330
    },
    {
      "id": "5a719d9aaff09e0000a1560f",
      "text": " \t[コサイン類似度が高いベクトルはどれくらい似ているか(岩波データサイエンス刊行イベントより) - Mi manca qualche giovedi`? http://d.hatena.ne.jp/n_shuyo/20160401/cosine_similarity]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517395354,
      "updated": 1539609790
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc494a2aff09e0000aed404",
      "text": "  >1000000 サンプルのうちコサイン類似度が 1/2 を超える割合を求めると、 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609763,
      "updated": 1539609848
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc494f1aff09e0000aed406",
      "text": "  > 10 次元 では 0.06 (約 1/17)、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609842,
      "updated": 1539609842
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc494f1aff09e0000aed407",
      "text": "  > 20 次元 では 0.01 (約 1/100)、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609842,
      "updated": 1539609842
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc494f1aff09e0000aed408",
      "text": "  > 30 次元 では 0.0021 (約 1/480)、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609842,
      "updated": 1539609842
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc494f1aff09e0000aed409",
      "text": "  > 40 次元 では 0.00042 (約 1/2400)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609842,
      "updated": 1539609843
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc494f3aff09e0000aed40a",
      "text": "  >100 次元 では、1000000個サンプリングした中にコサイン類似度が 1/2 以上になる点はなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609843,
      "updated": 1539609845
    },
    {
      "id": "5a71a163aff09e0000a15611",
      "text": "　 もちろん2次元では33%",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517396323,
      "updated": 1588912592
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4e1beaff09e00000c8d21",
      "text": "　関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588912575,
      "updated": 1588912575
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4df68aff09e00000c8d1b",
      "text": "　　https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1258610796969340928?s=21",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588911977,
      "updated": 1588912010
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4df8aaff09e00000c8d1c",
      "text": "　　[多様性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588912011,
      "updated": 1588912015
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4dfd9aff09e00000c8d1e",
      "text": "　　高次元空間でランダムな2つのベクトルを取った場合に、その2つがほぼ同じ方向である確率は、その2つがほぼ直交である確率に比べてとても小さい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588912089,
      "updated": 1588912093
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4dfe5aff09e00000c8d1f",
      "text": "　　次元(評価軸の本数)が増えると、ある人のスキルが別の人のスキルに対して完全に優越する状態が起こる確率が下がる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588912102,
      "updated": 1588912159
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4e047aff09e00000c8d20",
      "text": "　　　1次元で100%、2次元で50%、3次元で25%",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588912200,
      "updated": 1588912228
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4e19eaff09e000096e288",
      "text": "　　　[https://gyazo.com/1b7ed946d22e1cceca40118b9cc7ee6f]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588912542,
      "updated": 1588912542
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4e19eaff09e000096e289",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588912542,
      "updated": 1588912542
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb4df64aff09e00000c8d1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1588911973,
      "updated": 1588911973
    },
    {
      "id": "5a71a162aff09e0000a15610",
      "text": "\tほとんどすべての停留点は[鞍点]である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517396323,
      "updated": 1524477738
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb12eaff09e000094f309",
      "text": " \t10次元で99.8%",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478254,
      "updated": 1524478258
    },
    {
      "id": "5a71a1a5aff09e0000a15613",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517396389,
      "updated": 1517396389
    },
    {
      "id": "5a71a16caff09e0000a15612",
      "text": "\t特定の軸だけが大きいケースはほとんどない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517396333,
      "updated": 1517396400
    },
    {
      "id": "5a7151aeaff09e0000a155a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517375919,
      "updated": 1517375919
    },
    {
      "id": "5a71516aaff09e0000a155a2",
      "text": "[盲点カード] 19",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517375851,
      "updated": 1517375852
    },
    {
      "id": "5a71516aaff09e0000a155a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1517375851,
      "updated": 1517375851
    }
  ]
}